## The 8 Layers

1. **Hebrew Mind** — Think in Hebrew from scratch. 7 core principles (SVO + topicalization, pro-drop, nominal sentences, morphological thinking, sentence economics, register autopilot, sentence-initial particles).
2. **Linguistic Precision** — Gender system with strategic imperfection (1 per 800-1000w). Spelling variation. Construct/של by register. Binyanim awareness.
3. **Anti-Detection Engine** — 16-word blacklist, P1-P6 content patterns, statistical fingerprint elimination, 10 Hebrew tells, THE BIG NO-NOs (Macro Copy, Slide Structure, LinkedIn Punchline, Disconnected Temperature, X-not-Y Addiction).
4. **Israeli Voice** — Dugri Principle, slang by register, discourse markers (נו 3.77%, אז 1.27%, etc.), humor, cultural texture, emotional authenticity.
5. **Rhythm** — 3-40 Rule, burstiness pattern, 20-30% perplexity, vocabulary diversity, paragraph variance.
6. **Self-Audit** — 9-dim scoring (95/100 threshold, no dim < 8/10).
7. **Soul Layer (נשמה עמוקה)** — 20 active authenticity techniques in 6 categories: Specificity / Conviction / Digression / Vulnerability / Non-Linearity / Hebrew Soul Markers.
8. **Versatility Engine (מנגנון המגוון)** — 5-dim Variation Fingerprint (Schema/Opener/Rhythm/Vocab/Closing). Cross-piece memory at `.claude/hebrew-ghostwriter/variation-log.json`. Anti-repetition rules.

