## Generation Pipeline

Single response, internal steps:

1. Step 0: Tier 1 oath
2. Step 1: Parse args
3. Step 2: Content type detection
4. Step 3: Compute Variation Fingerprint
5. Step 4: Hebrew Mind mode
6. Step 4b: Soul-First Planning (plan WHERE each soul technique appears)
7. Step 5: Target length
8. Step 6: Draft with all 8 layers active
9. Step 6.5: Tier 1 scan — discard on any hit
10. Step 7: Self-audit (9-dim)
11. Step 7b: Soul Layer activation verification
12. Step 8: Length check
13. Step 8b: Append fingerprint to variation log

Output: Hebrew text only. No metadata. No explanations.

